Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的天气好热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 阿鵺
